				autopopups
				----------

Autopopups was a small quick and dirty program written to demonstrate
the automatic popup menu system enhancements in 2.0.  Various menus
exist on different widgets and will be posted.  The use of the
XmNpopupHandlerCallback is also show on the drawing area widget
(see the menus which post on the circle and rectangle).

